OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FAn inquiry into abuse at Muckamore
OL,7,FAbbey Hospital has found 'profound and
OL,8,Fdeeply troubling' failures in care.
OL,10,FThe inquiry report, published on
OL,11,FThursday, found that restrictive
OL,12,Fpractices were used inappropriately
OL,13,Fand that 'as needed' medication was
OL,14,Foverused and 'left some patients
OL,15,Fzombified'.
OL,17,FChairman of the inquiry Tom Kark KC
OL,18,Fsaid the people who lived at Muckamore
OL,19,Fand their families 'deserved better'.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
