OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FMuckamore Abbey, run by the Belfast
OL,7,FHealth and Social Care Trust, was a
OL,8,Fhospital in Co Antrim for adults with
OL,9,Fsevere learning disabilities and
OL,10,Fmental health needs.
OL,12,FThe inquiry examined allegations of
OL,13,Fabuse of patients at the facility.
OL,15,FIt was initially set up by former
OL,16,FHealth Minister Robin Swann and began
OL,17,Fhearing evidence in June 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
