FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781866972
OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FThe hospital has also been at the
OL,7,Fcentre of the UK's largest-ever police
OL,8,Finvestigation into the alleged abuse
OL,9,Fof vulnerable adults and a number of
OL,10,Fprosecutions are continuing.
OL,12,FPolice seized 300,000 hours of CCTV
OL,13,Ffootage, revealing what the inquiry
OL,14,Fheard was 'shocking abuse of
OL,15,Fvulnerable patients'.
OL,17,FThe inquiry's central finding was that
OL,18,Fa policy shift to move patients with
OL,19,Flearning disabilities and autism from
OL,20,Fhospital into community care was not
OL,21,Fmatched with investment.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
