PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781866972
OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FAs a result, many patients could not
OL,7,Fbe safely discharged due to a lack of
OL,8,Fcapacity in the community leading to
OL,9,Fdelays in resettlement, heightened
OL,10,Fdistress, and in some cases
OL,11,Freadmission.
OL,13,FThe inquiry also found that there was
OL,14,F"insufficient" staffing at all levels,
OL,15,Fleading to unsafe wards, and
OL,16,Frestrictive practices were used
OL,17,Finappropriately.
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@NO]
