PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781866972
OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FStaff instability, increased violence,
OL,7,Fhigh use of restrictive practices and
OL,8,Frepeated complaints were "visible and
OL,9,Fknown".
OL,11,FIt also found that "as needed"
OL,12,Fmedication was overused as a tool of
OL,13,Frestraint which left some patients
OL,14,F"zombified".
OL,16,FIt found that seclusion was misused as
OL,17,Fpunishment for so-called "bad
OL,18,Fbehaviour" and was not properly
OL,19,Fmonitored.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@FO]sD@TOUsD@^O]vD@AOUvD@KO]yD@
OL,26,AZOUzD@JO]
