OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FThere was a "closed culture" among
OL,7,Fstaff which discouraged reporting of
OL,8,Fpoor behaviour and many families said
OL,9,Fthey were frightened to complain in
OL,10,Fcase it impacted on the care their
OL,11,Frelatives received.
OL,26,@nD@MOUnD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
