PN,41507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781866972
OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FThe inquiry has made 106
OL,7,Frecommendations and proposes reforms
OL,8,Fin response to the "profound catalogue
OL,9,Fof failures", including "ineffective"
OL,10,Fexternal inspection regimes, and
OL,11,Fserious failures in governance within
OL,12,Fthe Belfast Health and Social Care
OL,13,FTrust which led to the erosion of
OL,14,Foversight at the care facility over
OL,15,Fmany years.
OL,17,FIt said the BHSCT treated each
OL,18,Fcomplaint in isolation, preventing any
OL,19,Frecognition of wider patterns emerging
OL,20,Fover time.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@LO]qD@YOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
