PN,41508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781866972
OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard oral evidence from
OL,7,F181 witnesses and 333 statements were
OL,8,Fconsidered.
OL,10,FA statement on behalf of the families
OL,11,Freleased by their solicitor following
OL,12,Fthe publication of the report said:
OL,13,F"The families said from the outset
OL,14,Fthat abuse was widespread and
OL,15,Fprolonged ... This report is the
OL,16,Fformal confirmation of a truth they
OL,17,Fhave lived with, and fought to expose,
OL,18,Ffor years."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
