PN,41509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1781866972
OL,3,CMuckamore inquiry finds 'profound and
OL,4,Cdeeply troubling' failures in care
OL,6,FSpeaking at the publication of the
OL,7,Freport, Mr Kark paid tribute to the
OL,8,Fresidents of Muckamore and their
OL,9,Ffamilies for being 'central to
OL,10,Funcovering the truth'.
OL,12,F"While the publication of this report
OL,13,Fcannot undo the harm suffered, it is
OL,14,Fmy hope that it will serve as a
OL,15,Fturning point", he said.
